high_descs: Turn left to reach the microwave.
Take out the fork from the microwave.
Head to the mug on the living room table to the left.
Put the fork in the mug.
Pick up the mug from the table.
Turn right to reach the countertop to the left of the sink.
Put the mug on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn left move forward enter into the kitchen then turn left to the microwave.
Take the fork out of the microwave.
Turn around walk toward the hall then turn right near to the mug.
Put the fork into the mug.
Pick up the mug from the desk.
Turn right and walk forward to the countertop.
Put the mug into the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the fork and mug into the sink.

high_descs: Walk into the kitchen and over to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, take out the fork from the microwave and close the door.
Walk out of the kitchen, over to the mug on the coffee table in the living room.
Place the fork into the black mug on the coffee table.
Pick up the mug with the fork inside of it from the coffee table.
Walk through the living room, into the kitchen, over to the countertop near the kitchen sink.
Place the mug onto the front left corner of the kitchen countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put a dirty Mug and Fork onto the kitchen CounterTop of the sink.
